s expired. Please buy a pack.'=>'订阅套餐已过期。请买一个套餐。','You must <a href="%s">purchase a subscription package</a> before posting'=>'您必须在发布前<a href="%s">购买订阅套餐</a>','Password has been reset. Please check your email.'=>'密码已被重置。 请查看你的邮箱。','Logout successful!'=>'注销成功！','Please fill all form fields'=>'请填写所有表单字段','WPUF Ajax Login'=>'WPUF Ajax登录','Go to Full Settings'=>'转到完整设置','Welcome to Awesomeness!'=>'欢迎来到Awesomeness！','Thank you!'=>'谢谢！','Skip this step'=>'跳过此步骤','Continue'=>'继续','Install neccessery pages on your site frontend.'=>'在您的网站前端安装neccessery页面。','Enable Payments'=>'启用付款','Basic Setting'=>'基本设置','Let\'s Go!'=>'开始吧！','No time right now? If you don’t want to go through the wizard, you can skip and return to the WordPress dashboard. Come back anytime if you change your mind!'=>'现在没时间? 如果您想跳过这个向导，您可以跳过并返回到 WordPress 仪表盘。如果你改变了主意，可以随时回来！','Welcome to the world of WPUF!'=>'欢迎来到WPUF的世界！','Return to the WordPress Dashboard'=>'返回到WordPress仪表板','Settings'=>'设置','Introduction'=>'介绍','enhanced selectPlease delete 1 character'=>'请删除1个字符','enhanced selectLoading failed'=>'加载失败','enhanced select%qty% results are available, use up and down arrow keys to navigate.'=>'%qty% 条结果可用，使用方向键的↑或↓键来选择。','enhanced selectOne result is available, press enter to select it.'=>'一个结果是可用的，按回车选择它。','What\'s New?'=>'有什么更新?','Change'=>'更改','Expire date:'=>'过期日期：','Subscription Details'=>'订阅详情','Registration Form'=>'注册表单','Coupons'=>'优惠券','Registration Forms'=>'注册表单','Recurring'=>'重复','Pack Title'=>'套餐标题','Post Date'=>'文章日期','Post URL'=>'文章网址','Post Title'=>'文章标题','Transaction Date'=>'交易日期','payer_address'=>'payer_address','Pack ID'=>'套餐 ID','Subtotal'=>'小计','Payment Status'=>'付款状态','WPUF Post Data'=>'WPUF发布数据','WPUF Transaction Data'=>'WPUF交易数据','Please see the <a href="https://mailchimp.com/legal/privacy/">MailChimp Privacy Policy</a> for more details.'=>'详情见 <a href="https://mailchimp.com/legal/privacy/"> mailchimp 隐私政策 </a>。','Available Modules'=>'可用模块','Payments'=>'支付','Transaction Details: we’ll ask you to enter this so we can, for instance, provide & regulate subscription packs that you bought and keep track of your payment details for subscription packs!'=>'交易明细：我们会要求您输入此内容，以便我们可以提供和管理您购买的订阅套餐，并跟踪订阅套餐的付款详细信息！','Password Reset Label:'=>'密码重置标签：','Password Reset Text:'=>'密码重置文本：','Log In Label:'=>'登录标签：','Remember Me Label:'=>'记住我标签：','Password Label:'=>'密码标签：','Username Label:'=>'用户名标签：','Log-in Text:'=>'登录文本：','Title:'=>'标题：','Log In'=>'登录','Password'=>'密码','Username'=>'用户名','Username or Email Address'=>'用户名或邮箱地址','Lost your password?'=>'忘记密码？','Register'=>'注册','As an example while using MailChimp for your marketing email automation service by integrating it with WP User Frontend, some of your data will be passed to MailChimp, including information required to process or support the email marketing services, such as name, email address and any other information that you intend to pass or collect including all collected information through subscription. '=>'例如，将MailChimp用于营销邮件自动化服务，将其与WP用户前端集成，您的一些数据将传递给MailChimp，包括处理或支持电子邮箱地址营销服务所需的信息，如姓名，电子邮箱地址地址和任何您打算传递或收集的其他信息，包括通过订阅收集的所有信息。 ','Username or E-mail:'=>'用户名或电子邮箱地址：','<strong>ERROR</strong>: The email could not be sent.Possible reason: your host may have disabled the mail() function.'=>'<strong>错误</strong>：邮件无法发送。可能的原因：您的主机可能禁用了mail() 功能。','Please enter your username or email address. You will receive a link to create a new password via email'=>'请输入您的用户名或电子邮箱地址。 您将收到一个链接以通过邮件创建新密码','If you create an account, we will store your name, address, email and phone number, which will be used to populate the form fields for future submissions.'=>'如果您创建了帐户，我们将存储您的姓名、地址、电子邮箱地址和电话号码，这些信息将用于填充表单字段以备将来提交。','Customer information like your name, email address, and billing and shipping information.'=>'客户信息，如您的姓名、电子邮箱地址，以及账单和配送信息。','When you fill up a form, we’ll ask you to provide information including your name, billing address, shipping address, email address, phone number, credit card/payment details and optional account information like username and password and any other form fields found in the form building options. We’ll use this information for purposes, such as, to:'=>'当您填写表单时，我们会要求您提供信息，包括您的姓名、账单地址、送货地址、电子邮箱地址、电话号码、信用卡/付款详情和可选的账户信息，如用户名和密码，以及在表单构建选项中找到的任何其他表单字段。我们会将这些信息用于以下目的：','We generally store information about you for as long as we need the information for the purposes for which we collect and use it, and we are not legally required to continue keeping it. For example, we will store form submission information for XXX years for tax, accounting and marketing purposes. This includes your name, email address and billing and shipping addresses.'=>'通常，我们会在我们收集和使用信息的目的所需要的时间范围内储存您的信息，但并没有法律要求我们需要继续储存这些信息。例如，我们会将表单提交信息存储XXX年，用于税务、会计和营销目的。这包括您的姓名、电子邮箱地址、账单和送货地址。','WP User Frontend'=>'前端用户中心','Create, edit, delete, manages your post, pages or custom post types from frontend. Create registration forms, frontend profile and more...'=>'从前端创建、编辑、删除、管理您的文章、页面或自定义文章类型。 创建注册表单、前端配置文件等等... ']];